file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /{country}:
    post:
      operationId: postCountry
      parameters:
        - name: country
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Example0:
              value: Poland
            Example1:
              value: UK
        - name: current-person
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Example0:
              value: alan
            Example1:
              value: bob
        - name: X-Forwarded-User
          in: header
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Example0:
              value: user1
            Example1:
              value: user2
         - name: cookie-param
         in: cookie
         required: true
         schema:
           type: string
         examples:
           Example0:
             value: cookie1
           Example1:
             value: cookie2
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Person'
            examples:
              Example0:
                value:
                  name: bob
                  age: 23
              Example1:
                value:
                  name: alan
                  age: 50
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          examples:
            Example0:
              value:
                Person:
                  name: michal
                  age: 40
            Example1:
                value:
                  Organization:
                    name: acme
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: query parameter current-person, Invalid
                        value for: body, Invalid value for: header X-Forwarded-User, Invalid value
                        for: cookie cookie-param'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    Entity:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Organization'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Person'
    Organization:
      required:
        - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
    Person:
      required:
        - name
        - age
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          type: integer
